# Runtime state - stays on this machine, never commit.
# Logs contain usernames/machine names; tenants.json contains account UPNs
# and tenant ids; settings.ini holds per-machine window/theme state (the app
# recreates it with defaults on first run).
Logs/
tenants.json
settings.ini
Script-Package*Setup.exe

# Icon source art + one-off build helper (the shipped app only needs Images/logo.*)
Script-Package-Studio.png
build-icon.ps1
